(10) Pursuant to sections 85-1101 to 85-1104, authorize out-of-state
institutions of higher or postsecondary education to offer courses or degree
programs in this state;

(b) Changes in the weighting of courses that may be necessary for reimbursable
educational units to properly reflect the role and mission of Nebraska community
colleges and the cost of providing such courses;
